{"tid":942660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【欺凌變殺人】保護兒子對抗惡霸 好爸爸慘遭割耳痛毆致死","createTime":"2018-12-16T02:51:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-17T00:19:23.000Z","uid":130626,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"8df91a2a08998b301d584963f8af053b6c65aabc","tid":942660,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T02:51:00.000Z","msg":"英國一名青年在街上遭人欺凌襲擊，其父聞聲救子，但被斬至重傷，雙耳被割下，留院兩星期後終告不治。<br />\n事發在上月27日晚上約10時半，一家居於布萊克本(Blackburn)的24歲青年阿山(Ahsan Choudry)外出買煙，返到家門前遭人襲擊，他42歲的父親喬德賴(Sajed Choudry)聽到其呼救聲，立即衝出去救他，但兇徒手持利刀，兩父子不敵，喬德賴被割掉雙耳、被打至腦出血和肺部塌下，陷入昏迷。而阿山半隻手掌被斬掉，頭部亦有刀傷。<br />\n喬德賴的22歲女兒說，事件源於阿山在校遭人欺凌的問題，喬德賴半年前也曾遇襲。她表示現在感到極度恐慌，她們一家在那條街住了15年，從未遇過如此兇殘的事。<br />\n警方拘捕了3名男子和一名13歲男童，他們將被控謀殺。<br />\n英國《每日郵報》<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LJJTrjA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLJJTrjA.png&h=0848404c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eR8cGSW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeR8cGSW.png&h=fac2f4ce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"36524a40cf33014390dcfa3e215707f3b17706aa","tid":942660,"uid":121146,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T02:53:14.000Z","msg":"又斬手又斬耳  兇手會係乜人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"561d3c53c94dcca71facaece5ff14d0cdbaeba08","tid":942660,"uid":40470,"like":4,"dislike":44,"score":-40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T02:53:55.000Z","msg":"煙剷就抵撚死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"370a774ee55a50feeb694f567c75a71b8dc6c301","tid":942660,"uid":219141,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T02:54:04.000Z","msg":"好撚慘 救個仔都要用命換<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b996bfd09923349583b70cc0a34c8cc219387150","tid":942660,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T02:54:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" clas